!!!
html
	head
		meta(charset="utf-8")
		meta(name="description", content="#{blogDescription}")
		meta(name="keywords", content="#{blogKeywords}")
		title #{blogName}
		link(type="image/x-icon", rel="shortcut icon", href="/favicon.ico")
		link(rel="alternate", type="application/rss+xml", title="TooBug", href="./rss/rss.xml")
		link(rel="stylesheet", href="./css/light.css")
		link(rel="stylesheet", href="./js/prettify/prettify.css")
		script(src="./js/prettify/prettify.js")
		script(src="./js/jquery/jquery-1.7.2.min.js")
		script(src="./js/index.js")
	body
		header
			div#logo
				a(href="/") #{blogName}
			nav
				ul
					li
						a(href="./index.html") Index<br />首页
					li
						a(href="./about.html") About<br />关于

		section#sidebar
			div#intro
				p
					| <strong>TooBug</strong>，前端工程师，目前就职于<a href="http://cdc.tencent.com" target="_blank">腾讯CDC</a>。关注体验设计，关注大前端生态圈。
				p
					| 新浪微博：<a href="http://weibo.com/toooobug" target="_blank">@TooBug</a>
				p
					| 腾讯微博：<a href="http://t.qq.com/TooBug" target="_blank">@TooBug</a>
				p
					| GitHub：<a href="https://github.com/toooobug" target="_blank">@TooBug</a>


		section#content
			div#article
				for blog in blogList
					div.indexarticle
						h1
							a(href="./article/#{blog.url}.html") #{blog.title}
						p
							em #{blog.pubDate}
						| !{blog.summary}
						div.articlemore
							a(href="./article/#{blog.url}.html") 继续阅读

		div#pagination
			- for(var i=0;i<pageCount;i++){
				- if(i)
					- var str='_page'+(i+1);
				- else
					- var str = '';
				<a href="index#{str}.html">#{i+1}</a>
			- }

		div#foot
			p
				| Powered by <a href="https://github.com/TooooBug/solo"  target="_blank">Solo</a>